the one i love is a 2014 american science-fiction thriller film directed by charlie mcdowell and written by justin &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; , the film stars mark duplass and elisabeth moss . the film had its world premiere at 2014 sundance film festival on january 21 , 2014 . it was released on august 1 , 2014 through video on demand prior to a limited release on august 22 , 2014 , by radius-twc .